09-part-one |accessdate=July 11, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6iJvzuEOH?url=http://www.noripcord.com/features/top-50-albums-2009-part-one |archivedate=June 17, 2016 |url-status=live }}\n* {{cite web|ref=harv|last=Ford|first=Winston \"Stone\"|url=http://www.thecouchsessions.com/2010/02/interview-cognito-mos-defs-documentiarian-and-curator-of-ecstatic-moments/|date=February 2010|website=The Couch Sessions|title=Interview: Cognito, Mos Def\u2019s Documentiarian and curator of Ecstatic Moments|accessdate=August 29, 2018}}\n* {{cite web|ref=harv |last=Gundersen |first=Edna |authorlink=Edna Gundersen |year=2009 |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2009-06-07-mos-def_N.htm |title=Mos Def is Most Thoughtful as He Focuses on Myriad Projects |work=[[USA Today]] |accessdate=June 4, 2016 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6iJw87Vtd?url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2009-06-07-mos-def_N.htm |archivedate=June 17, 2016 |url-status=live }}\n* {{cite web |ref=harv |last=Harling |first=Danielle |year=2009 |url=http://www.hiphopdx.com/index/news/id.10231/title.drake-mos-def-and-more-receive-grammy-nominations |title=Drake, Mos Def And More Receive Grammy Nominations |work=HipHopDX |accessdate=February 20, 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6iJwGWOEJ?url=http://hiphopdx.com/news/id.10231/title.drake-mos-def-and-more-receive-grammy-nominations |archivedate=June 17, 2016 |url-status=dead }}\n* {{cite web|ref=harv |last=Henderson |first=Eric |year=2009 |url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/mos-def-the-ecstatic/1774 |title=Mos Def: The Ecstatic |work=[[Slant Magazine]] |accessdate=April 21, 2013 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6G3hvIINo?url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/mos-def-the-ecstatic/1774 |archivedate=April 22, 2013 |url-status=live }}\n* {{cite magazine|ref=harv |last=Hoard |first=Christian |year=2009 |title=The Ecstatic : Mos Def : Review |magazine=[[Rolling Stone]] |url=https://www.rolling